                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p class="answer">
                                    <span class="highlight">Minimal-incision</span> breast reduction focuses on reducing breast size with <span class="bold">smaller scars</span> and less invasive techniques. Approaches like the <span class="highlight">lollipop incision</span> (around the areola and vertically down) or <span class="bold">liposuction-only</span> methods are common. These techniques minimize visible scarring while achieving a <span class="italic">natural, lifted breast shape</span>.
